{"word":"ψέλλιον 1","slug":"ψέλλιον 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n115414\" key=\"ye/llion1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ψέλλιον</orth> <sense id=\"n115414.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καλοῦσι τὸ ἄκρον· ὅθεν καὶ ἡμεῖς τὴν ἐπ᾽ ἄκρων χειλέων λεγομένην προσῳδίαν ψιλὴν ἐκαλέσαμεν, ὥς φησι Τρύφων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0708.tlg001:p.143V\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ammon.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Diff.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.143V.</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψέλιον</foreign> is distd. from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψάλιον</foreign> by <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0708.tlg001:p.142\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ammon.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Diff.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.142</biblScope> </bibl> V., Ptol.Asc.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0708.tlg001:p.396H\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.396H.</biblScope></bibl>, but is the later form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ψάλιον</foreign> acc. to Moer.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0708.tlg001:p.420P\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">p.420P.</biblScope></bibl>, Sch.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg015.perseus-grc1:792\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">792</biblScope> </bibl> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἔστι δὲ ψέλιον ὁ κρίκος τοῦ χαλινοῦ, ἢ ἁπλῶς ὁ κρίκος</etym>) and this may be the meaning in <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ PCair.Zen.\">PCair.Zen.</a></title_> l. c.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}